4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge who wish to become cybersecurity specialists. The course spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Upon completion, participants receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. The program is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). Stop.